" 很棒的插件，解决了我的代码输入时光标移动问题（不使用键盘右区），
" http://blog.csdn.net/simple_the_best/article/details/53132943

" 插入模式：光标移动，删除
inoremap <C-h> <Left>
inoremap <C-j> <Down>
inoremap <C-k> <Up>
inoremap <C-l> <Right>
inoremap <C-s> <Home>
inoremap <C-e> <End>
inoremap <C-d> <Delete>

inoremap <C-n> <Backspace>
inoremap <C-m> <Delete>

" 插入模式：返回普通状态,Back
inoremap <C-b> <Esc>

" 普通模式：关闭文件,Quit
nnoremap <Space>q  :q<CR>
nnoremap <Space>Q  :qa!<CR>

" 普通模式：快速翻页，Up，Down
nnoremap <Space>d  <C-d>
nnoremap <Space>u  <C-u>

" 以下还用不到=====================================

" clear the highlighted search result
nnoremap <Space>sc :nohlsearch<CR>

nnoremap <Space>fs :w<CR>


" Quit visual mode
vnoremap v <Esc>

" Move to the start of line
nnoremap H ^

" Move to the end of line
nnoremap L $

" Redo
nnoremap U <C-r>

" Yank to the end of line
nnoremap Y y$

" Auto indent pasted text
nnoremap p p=`]<C-o>

" Window operation
nnoremap <Space>ww <C-W>w
nnoremap <Space>wd <C-W>c
nnoremap <Space>wj <C-W>j
nnoremap <Space>wk <C-W>k
nnoremap <Space>wh <C-W>h
nnoremap <Space>wl <C-W>l
nnoremap <Space>w= <C-W>=
nnoremap <Space>ws <C-W>s
nnoremap <Space>w- <C-W>s
nnoremap <Space>wv <C-W>v
nnoremap <Space>w\| <C-W>v

" Tab operation
nnoremap <Space>tn gt
nnoremap <Space>tp gT
